Test::Simpler version 0.000007


All the tasty syntactic simplicity of Test::Simple,
with all of goodness and reporting power of Test::More


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

None.


